flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    TileSvc[Tile Server]
    TileStore[(Tile Object Store)]
    CDN[CDN]
    Routing[Routing Service<br/>CH / ALT]
    RoadGraph[(Road Network<br/>Graph)]
    Geocoder[Geocoder]
    SearchIdx[(Address<br/>Search Index)]
    Traffic[Traffic Aggregator<br/>5-min windows]
    Pings[(GPS Ping<br/>event stream)]

    Client -->|tile z/x/y| CDN
    CDN -.->|miss| TileSvc
    TileSvc --> TileStore
    Client -->|route req| Routing
    Routing --> RoadGraph
    Client -->|geocode| Geocoder
    Geocoder --> SearchIdx
    Pings -.->|anonymized| Traffic
    Traffic -.->|edge weights| RoadGraph

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class TileSvc,CDN,Routing,Geocoder,Traffic service
    class TileStore,RoadGraph,SearchIdx,Pings store
